    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Suy ra } \\cos \\widehat{EPF} = \\cos(\\overline{PE}, \\overline{PF}) = \\frac{\\overline{PE} \\cdot \\overline{PF}}{|\\overline{PE}| \\cdot |\\overline{PF}|} = \\frac{(-4) \\cdot (4) + 0 \\cdot 0 + (-1,2) \\cdot (-1,2)}{\\sqrt{(-4)^2 + 0^2 + (-1,2)^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{4^2 + 0^2 + (-1,2)^2}} = -\\frac{91}{109}.\n$$"
